description: Farm Fresh, Seasonal Eats from the Clif Family BruschetteriaThe Clif Family Bruschetteria serves a seasonal menu of bruschetta, porchetta, farm fresh salads and rotisserie chicken.Executive Chef John McConnell has embraced a traditional yet fresh approach to Northern Italian cuisine, fueled by ingredients from the certified organic Clif Family Farm and local purveyors.You can usually find us parked outside of Velo Vino at 709 Main Street, St. Helena, CA.Tuesday through Sunday, 11:30 to 4PMFollow us @clif_foodtruck
name: Clif Family Bruschetteria
